graph TD
    A[Start: Update Server URL] --> B[Create Web Connection]
    B --> C[Send Update Request to Server]
    C --> D{Request Successful?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Read Server Response]
    E --> F[Log Success Message]
    F --> G[Return Success]
    D -- No --> H[Log Failure Message]
    H --> I[Return Failure]
    C -- Connection Error --> J[Log Error Message]
    J --> I
    G --> K[End: Success]
    I --> L[End: Failed]